2001-2443 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE of Louisiana v. Johnnel GREEN. No. 2002-KK-2443. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re State of Louisiana; — Plaintiff; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Orleans, Criminal District Court Div. C, No. 428-031; to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Circuit, No. 2002-K-1437.

Denied.

VICTORY, J., would grant the writ. TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ. KNOLL, J., would grant the writ.
